        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
                    VeriDoc HR is a verification solution designed to track employees’ working hours and eliminate
                    timesheet fraud. Due to an increased number of employees working from home, the solution can now
                    be applied to a remote-based workforce as well as traditional businesses.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
